What you need to know:

He denied the second count of abuse of position of authority contrary to section 24(2) (a) of the Sexual Offenses Act.Mr Ayub Nyaga Kamau, 28, who is attached to Kiunga Camp in Lamu East denied three counts among them defiling a Standard Four girl aged 15 years between July and October 6, 2020 within Kiunga area.